{"tid":1716445,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰略post]新職業-通訊師 大學撚同我入黎 自己學校自己救","createTime":"2019-11-13T10:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T11:24:15.000Z","uid":306759,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"68d997b1e860b12f28552916fb704b049c17568b","tid":1716445,"uid":306759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:45:28.000Z","msg":"（代post）<br />\n<br />\n唔想輸得咁慘，唔該同我睇到落底。<br />\n<br />\n知唔知琴晚中大輸乜嘢?係樣樣都輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，班狗有槍、有training、有組織，班同學仔得把遮喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!<br />\n<br />\n知唔知班狗部署行動一定要乜嘢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重要嘅嘢講三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;無線電(radio)&gt;&gt;&gt;</strong></span>呀<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;無線電(radio)&gt;&gt;&gt;</strong></span>呀<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;無線電(radio)&gt;&gt;&gt;</strong></span>呀<br />\n<br />\n介紹番先，任何無線電通訊系統都係由兩部分組成，一部分係<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">發射</span></strong>，另一部分係<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">接收</span></strong>。 發射信號站同booster基本上都係安裝喺建築物入面同外面。<br />\n<br />\n室內嘅booster信號個range比較細，所以通常喺每層樓都至少有一個，一般安裝喺天花位置或者假天花入面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aj9vktq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAj9vktq.jpg&h=c6017652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hawp9mM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhawp9mM.jpg&h=1cfd04a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n室外嘅發射站就一般安裝喺天台，負責提供信號畀馬路或者其他附近嘅室外地方。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sXvRPmS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsXvRPmS.jpg&h=b40d9235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗱以我所知，呢啲裝置有幾個部分係要特別保護嘅<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>1.電線<br />\n2.訊號線<br />\n3.主機<br />\n4.樓層總電掣</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n住喺中大科大嶺南樹仁嘅人聽住，你哋地方比較偏僻，只要發射站有任何損壞/運作唔到，班狗就冇辦法做任何部署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以住喺呢四大嘅每一個人， 快啲化身通訊師， 即刻同我搵下每一層個無線電booster嘅位置!<br />\n<br />\n當然，唔係呢四大嘅人都可以諗下點發揮你地嘅作用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>大家千祈唔好搞呢啲裝置呀</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!!!!咁班狗先可以通訊無障礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 唔係呢方面專家，有錯請更正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ebe0be13e57a6215f39011714aff512a83df051","tid":1716445,"uid":58351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:46:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"50b77257fc3693e1dbe44887e12d99afee01bbd6","tid":1716445,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:47:20.000Z","msg":"爆基站你都死架喎"},{"pid":"05a9be0f1268fe2d710d5cf97b4fd97044321815","tid":1716445,"uid":125958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:47:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f436b1f01db11d359088aa0b7af4c8ec4dadc86c","tid":1716445,"uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:47:59.000Z","msg":"班狗用自己radio，你搞cell site想斷自己網 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fe7096057298e0d2d0b1333ca60e012703ce18","tid":1716445,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T10:49:18.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"8de07c8c68ee086754d34d57a6d8aecdbffb4850","tid":1716445,"uid":150930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,